Detailed Description

GENERATED CLASS.

Represents the <machines> XML element in memory. DTD declaration:

 <!ELEMENT machines (machine*)>
 <!ATTLIST machines
      banner-comment      CDATA     IMPLIED
      right-comment       CDATA     "&#10;" >
